==Ditso tsa Hotele==
Hotele ya''' kwa maphothophothong a Victoria '''  ke hotele ya ditso kwa maphothophothong a Victoria mo, Zimbabwe. Hotele e e lebaganye le kgoro ya bobedi gape le  borogo jwa maphothophotho a Victoriac go tsweng kwa a elelelang teng.Hotele e e itsege ka leina la“the grand old lady of the Falls” ebile e mo lefelona la diphologolo la maphothophotho a victoria.

Hotele e e butswe ka ngwaga wa 1904 go fa bapagami ba ba neng ba fetla ka seporo se se neng se sa tswa go agiwa, nngwe ya maano a seporo sa Cape go ya Cairo. Moragonyana e ne ya nna sefetla sa makwalo a BOAC a ditirelo gareng ga[[ Southampton]] le [[ Aferika Borwa]]. Hotele e e santse e kile ya fa baeti ba bogosi boroko mo makgetlhong a mmalwa, ba akaretsa King George VI ka kgwedi ya Moranang ngwaga wa 1947.<ref>[http://www.tothevictoriafalls.com/vfpages/tourism/royalvisit.html To the Victoria Falls website: Royal visits]</ref>

Hotele e ntse e ele lefelo la bokopanelo jwa sepoloti. Ka ngwaga wa 1949 Roy Welensky o ne  rulaganya bokopano gone koo go bua ka ka tlholo ya Federation of Rhodesia le Nyasaland, gape ka ngwaga wa 1963 bokopano jwa kwa hoteleng e e kwa maphothophothong e ne ya baka kgaogano ya bokopano.

Hotele ke leloko la dihotele tse di eteletseng pele mo dtlhopheng tsa lefatsheng. E laolwa ke kompone ya African Sun Limited.

==Diponagadi tsa Hotele==
Se se dirang gore hotele e e itsege lefatshe ka bophara ke boleng jo bo kwa godimo jwa thuso e e fiwang bajanala fa ba etetse maphothophotho.Go nale mantlo a borobalo a maemo a a kwa godimo le dijo tse di kgatlhang leitlho go leba.Fa tsatsi le phirima bajanala ba rata go kgweediwa ka mekoro go ya go bona bontle jwa tlholego le diphologolo ka mefutla ya tsone.

